For vim syntax coloring copy mtc.vim in /usr/share/vim/vimcurrent/syntax directory for Linux or /usr/share/vim/vim73/syntax under cygwin.

Then edit /usr/share/vim/vimcurrent/filetype.vim or /usr/share/vim/vim73/filetype.vim and add these 2 lines :
" MultitaskC
au BufNewFile,BufRead *.llC,*.ec,*.mtc          setf mtc
